Package edu.uw.pce.advjava.sighting

Record Class UfoSighting

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
edu.uw.pce.advjava.sighting.UfoSighting
Record Components:
id - sighting identifier
observationTime - time of observation
dateDocumented - date observation was reported
season - season the observation occurred in
countyCode - country code of the country the observation occurred in
region - region the observation occurred in
local - local the observation occurred in
latitude - latitude of observation
longitude - longitude of observation
ufoShape - shape observed
encounterDuration - duration of observation (seconds)
description - description of observation
public record UfoSighting(long id, LocalDateTime observationTime, LocalDate dateDocumented, Season season, String countyCode, String region, String local, double latitude, double longitude, UfoShape ufoShape, double encounterDuration, String description) extends Record
Record of a UFO sighting.
